	(text "Power & PDN - rail summary\nRail         | Nominal       | Notes\nVDD / VDDQ   | 1.2 V         | DRAM core + I/O (VDDQ tied to VDD in v1)\nVPP          | 2.5 V         | DRAM wordline boost\nVREFCA       | 0.6 V (VDD/2) | Command/address reference, external (VREFDQ is on-die on DDR4)\nVDDSPD       | (confirm)     | SPD EEPROM supply\nVSS / GND    | 0 V           | Ground\n\nScope: this sheet covers power nets and references only -\nno CA / data / SPD / connector signals here.\nDecoupling/bypass and PDN (decap selection + placement, plane assignment)\nare not enumerated in v1; PDN design is layout-stage work."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
